div.h3: Transform Your Raspberry Pi into a Digital Photo Frame
div.p: The Raspberry Pi is an affordable, compact device that can easily turn a monitor into a customisable digital photo frame, displaying your favorite photos in a continuous slideshow. Ill be using Immich, a self-hosted photo and video management solution, to achievethis.

div.h3: I created a public API that exposes WCA competition results
div.p: The World Cube Association governs competitions for mechanical puzzles that are operated by twisting groups of pieces, commonly known as twisty puzzles.

div.h3: How I got to solving the Rubiks cube in under 30 seconds
div.p: About six months ago I wrote a blog post about how I got to solving the Rubiks cube in under 60 seconds consistently. Since then, I have been working on improving and getting even fastersolves.

div.h3: Unraveling the Magic of Composition over Inheritance
div.p: Composition over inheritance is a principle in programming that emphasizes the use of object composition instead of class inheritance to achieve code maintainability. While inheritance can be useful in certain scenarios, it can also lead to tight coupling and inflexible designs.
